snippet.title: Wrath of Salaar | Music By Ravi Basrur | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
Witness the vengeance, feel the power - Wrath of Salaar 

From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the First Single of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films.
 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Dec 22, 2023.

Ravi Basrur Music Team
Composed by: Ravi Basrur 
Additional music by 
Yair Albeg Wein and CRETIC,
Music licensing courtesy of Songs To Your Eyes Ltd.

snippet.title: RBI Bans PayTM in INDIA | PayTM FASTag, Wallet, UPI Going To Close After 29th Feb 2024 | SidTalk
snippet.description:
Hey Guys,
In this video you'll get to know that RBI bans PayTM Payments Bank & Its services like: PayTM UPI, PayTM Wallet, PayTM FASTag, NCMC Card, Prepaid Cards, etc.
Other paytm service: PayTM QR, POS Machine, Soundbox, Payment Gateway will work?
Action against Paytm Payments Bank Ltd under Section 35A of the Banking Regulation Act, 1949
Explained: Why RBI Has Put Restrictions On Paytm Payments Bank
Common question by PayTM customers:
My NCMC Card will stop working?,
My POS Machine/Soundbox not work?,
My Fast Tag will stop working?

PayTM said services will work as Paytm to expand its existing relationships with leading third-party banks to distribute payments and financial services products.

Chapters:
0:00 Intro
0:28 RBI Bans PayTM services
0:48 PayTM Business Timeline
1:40 PayTM One97 Communication Services
3:29 RBI Ban Rules Point Wise
4:20 PayTM Reply on RBI Ban
6:21 What to do if i'm using PayTM Services?

Or a walking talking green flag Raghav (Played by Vishal Vashishtha, known for his role in Amazon MiniTV's Hustlers) she met from Jeevansaathi and went on a couple of dates with. snippet.description:
The Ministry Of Ungentlemanly Warfare ‚Äì In theaters April 19. Starring Henry Cavill, Eiza Gonz√°lez, Alan Ritchson, Alex Pettyfer, Hero Fiennes Tiffin, Babs Olusanmokun, Henrique Zaga, Til Schweiger, with Henry Golding, and Cary Elwes.

Subscribe to the LIONSGATE YouTube Channel for the latest movies trailers, clips, and more: https://bit.ly/2Z6nfym

https://TheMinistyOfUngentlemanlyWarfare.movie
https://www.instagram.com/ungentlemanlywarfare
https://www.facebook.com/UngentlemanlyWarfare

#UngentlemanlyWarfare

Based upon recently declassified files of the British War Department and inspired by true events, THE MINISTRY OF UNGENTLEMANLY WARFARE is an action-comedy that tells the story of the first-ever special forces organization formed during WWII by UK Prime Minister Winston Churchill and a small group of military officials including author Ian Fleming. The top-secret combat unit, composed of a motley crew of rogues and mavericks, goes on a daring mission against the Nazis using entirely unconventional and utterly ‚Äúungentlemanly‚Äù fighting techniques. Ultimately their audacious approach changed the course of the war and laid the foundation for the British SAS and modern Black Ops warfare.

snippet.title: Apple Vision Pro review: magic, until it‚Äôs not
snippet.description:
Apple‚Äôs long-awaited entry into the world of computers you wear on your face is here. Apple claims that the Vision Pro, a VR headset that starts at $3,499, is the beginning of something called ‚Äúspatial computing,‚Äù which basically boils down to running apps all around you. The Verge‚Äôs Editor-in-Chief Nilay Patel answers all your Vision Pro questions. #Apple #Technology #AppleVisionPro

Read more: https://trib.al/oniBlvx

Listen to The Vergecast: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pANxZ62BtBo

Kisi ki tashreef mei dum hi nahi 
Cash ki kami hogi taish ki kami nahi hai
Tere bhai ki life mei aish ki kami nahi hai

Ok report 
Jacket dekh, jeb mei pada hua packet dekh 
Ok report

Ok report

Ok report
Joote dekh, joote se kitne soote dekh 
Ok report

Gali ka leader apna hi bhai hai
Parking apni best lagayi hai
Poora din aaj chaud mei ghumenge
Monday hai aaj chest lagayi hai

Momos mei laal wali chatni laga
‚ÄúGaadi tera bhai chalayega‚Äù
Achha? toh apni chala

Padte hai kitne guddi pe gin 
Road pe chalte hai buddhi ke bin

Khaie Digitally Presented by Sparx Smartphones #shinewithsparx
Get Ready to be Enthralled by 'Khaie' - Brought to You by Geo TV with the Cutting-Edge Innovation of Sparx Smartphone as the Exclusive Digital Presenting Partner. A Spectacular Journey Awaits

The story is a revenge saga that unfolds against the backdrop of the ancient tradition of Khaie, where the male members of an enemy's family are eliminated to stop the continuation of their lineage.  At the center of this age-old vendetta are Darwesh Khan, Duraab Khan, and his son Channar Khan, with Zamdaa, the daughter of Darwesh, bearing the heaviest consequences.  
Darwesh Khan is haunted by his father's murder at the hands of Duraab Khan. Seeking a peaceful life, Darwesh aims to broker a truce to end generational enmity. However, suspicions arise, and Duraab Khan and his son Channar Khan doubt Darwesh's intentions for peace.
Despite the genuine efforts of Darwesh, a kind-hearted man with a message for peace, a tragic turn of events unfolds during a celebration at Darwesh's home, causing immense suffering for Zamdaa and her family.
Will Zamdaa bow down in front of her enemies? If not, then will Zamdaa be able to take revenge on her family culprits? Will Zamdaa find allies in her journey, or will she face her enemies alone?

Directed By: Syed Wajahat Hussain

Subscribe Drishti Teaching Exams Channel :

Presenting the interim Union Budget in Parliament this morning, Union Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman announced that there would be no change in tax rates for direct and indirect taxes, including import duties. Meanwhile, the fiscal deficit for 2024-25 is estimated at 5.1 per cent of GDP against 5.8 per cent in the current financial year.

snippet.title: Pariksha Pe Charcha 2024 LIVE | PM Modi interacts with students, teachers & parents on exams
snippet.description:
Prime Minister Narendra Modi interacted with students, teachers and parents at Bharat Mandapam in New Delhi during the 7th edition of Pariksha Pe Charcha (PPC). He also took a walkthrough of the art and crafts exhibition showcased on the occasion. PPC is a movement driven by Prime Minister Narendra Modi's efforts to bring together students, parents, teachers and society to foster an environment where each child's unique individuality is celebrated, encouraged and allowed to express itself fully.

Addressing the gathering of students, teachers and parents, the Prime Minister Narendra Modi mentioned the creations by the students in the exhibition where they have expressed aspirations and concepts like New National Education Policy in various shapes. He said these exhibits reflect what the new generations think about various topics and what solutions they have for these issues.
